The paper deals with mechanism design and revenue optimization in auctions, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). The use of a third-party data provider involves the manipulation and analysis of data, which could fall under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves optimization and analysis of revenue, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or information theory (cs.IT).
